quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  14,22,"Mi isuyya lameô, a d yini Cciîan: \"Öebbi, d ûûeê, Iweââd awen lemâahda n tidep. Weââde$ awen, $uôe$ kwen. Ur sâi$ adabu fellawen, siwa anecced nnwen. Tu$em awal iw. Ur iyi plummut, lummet iman nnwen. Ur zmire$ a kwen âawne$, ur tezmirem ad iyi tâawnem. Nekôe$ wid iyi tepcarakem, zik. I imednas, s tidep, aâaqeb aqeôêan"
  14,23,"Ad skecmen wid iumnen, ixeddmen ayen ilhan, ar leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen, ad wekkôen dinna, s wannuf n Mass nnsen. Azul nnsen dinna d: \"tifrat"
  14,24,"Day ur twalav ara, amek id Ifka Öebbi amedya? Awal lâali am ttejôa lâali, iéuôan is ôûan, iferkawen is di tegnewt"
  14,25,"Teppak ed lfakia s, di yal imir, s wannuf n Mass is. Ippawi d Öebbi imedyaten i imdanen, amar a d mmektin"
  14,26,"Amedya n wawal ucmit, am ttejôa tucmip, teqlaâ sennig wakal, war leqôaô"
  14,27,"Öebbi Itebbit wid iumnen s wawal utebbet, di tmeddurt n ddunit akked laxeôt. Öebbi Itellif imednas. Öebbi Ixeddem ayen i S ihwan"